---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <article class="prose measure">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>About this site</h1>
    <p>
      This is a reading log — a place to keep my book reviews and the notes I
      scribble in the margins. It started as a backfill of my Goodreads
      reviews and grows from here.
    </p>
    <p>
      <em>Replace this text with your own.</em> Tell people who you are, what
      you read, and what your ratings mean.
    </p>
    <h2>How the stars work</h2>
    <p>
      Five stars, halves allowed. Roughly: ★ couldn't finish · ★★ disappointing
      · ★★★ worthwhile · ★★★★ very good · ★★★★★ a favorite.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
